      • DataFileMetaData

        public DataFileMetaData(java.lang.String dataFilePath,
                        java.lang.String dateDirectoryPath,
                        int dataGroupID,
                        int year,
                        int day)
        Creates a DataFileMetaData object, defaults the QC file path to null and others to that given.
        Parameters:
        dataFilePath - - full path to the data file
        dateDirectoryPath - - path to the data file's date directory (e.g. ".../2015/001/")
        dataGroupID - - unique ID associated with the combination of the year and day
        year - - the Gregorian year the data file is relevant to
        day - - the Gregorian day of the year the data file is relevant to

      • DataFileMetaData

        public DataFileMetaData(java.lang.String dataFilePath,
                        java.lang.String qcFilePath,
                        java.lang.String dateDirectoryPath,
                        int dataGroupID,
                        int year,
                        int day)
        Creates a DataFileMetaData object initialized with the given metadata.
        Parameters:
        dataFilePath - - full path to the data file
        qcFilePath - - full path to the QC file associated to the data file
        dateDirectoryPath - - path to the data file's date directory (e.g. ".../2015/001/")
        dataGroupID - - unique ID associated with the combination of the year and day
        year - - the Gregorian year the data file is relevant to
        day - - the Gregorian day of the year the data file is relevant to
